race.comment: MONTERREY (4) missed the placings two runs back then improved last start but found a couple better over 1710m at Laurel, beaten 2.25 lengths. Has the talent to take care of this field. TASK FORCE (2) was out of the money when resuming from a spell last start over 1609m at Laurel, beaten 18 lengths. Fitter so expect a better run this time. PICO PLAT (3) was never in contention last time over 1609m at Laurel (Dirt) when he finished eighth, beaten 32 lengths. Among the chances in what looks a nice race for him. ZAPTASTIC (1) was never in contention last time over 1308m at this track (Dirt) when he finished eighth, beaten 16 lengths. This looks a nice race so expect him to finish closer.
